<item>
            <title>[LOG4J2-3650] Release 2.20.0 missing artifacts</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LOG4J2-3650</link>
                <project id="12310790" key="LOG4J2">Log4j 2</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It looks like the new 2.20.0 release didn&apos;t publish the log4j-core-&amp;lt;version&amp;gt;-tests.jar files that were in the previous release.  Can these files be published?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://repo1.maven.org/maven2/org/apache/logging/log4j/log4j-core/2.19.0/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://repo1.maven.org/maven2/org/apache/logging/log4j/log4j-core/2.19.0/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://repo1.maven.org/maven2/org/apache/logging/log4j/log4j-core/2.20.0/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://repo1.maven.org/maven2/org/apache/logging/log4j/log4j-core/2.20.0/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
</description>
